    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Solid and dependable \u2014 this car is priced to reflect its honest, fair condition! It's a great opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer who wants a functional, drivable vehicle without the premium price tag. The car shows normal wear consistent with its age and use \u2014 you'll notice some cosmetic imperfections on the exterior and interior signs of everyday life, but the fundamentals are there. Whether you're looking for a reliable commuter or a project car to spruce up, this one deserves a good look. Come see it in person and judge for yourself!",
