    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly & Ready for a New Owner \u2014 Priced Honestly for Its Condition! \u2014 If you're a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for an affordable entry-level vehicle, this could be your next project! This car is in poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for a buyer comfortable with repairs. What it lacks in polish, it makes up for in affordability and potential! Priced transparently at $6,000 to reflect exactly what you're getting \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for your needs!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want buyers to have a clear picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and paint fading across various panels. The interior has seen better days, with worn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs. This listing is best suited for someone looking for a project vehicle, a parts car, or a very budget-conscious buyer who is comfortable with the car's current state. No attempts have been made to hide or minimize the condition \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage an in-person inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Choice at an Honest Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is ready to get you where you need to go! It runs and drives well, making it a reliable option for daily use. The exterior shows some visible wear consistent with its age \u2014 expect minor scratches and small blemishes here and there \u2014 and the interior has normal signs of use, but everything is functional. Mechanically, it's in decent shape and has been honestly priced to reflect its condition. If you're looking for a practical, no-nonsense vehicle without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look! Come see it in person and judge for yourself. \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what you can expect. The exterior shows some signs of normal use \u2014 there are a few minor scratches and light scuffs consistent with everyday driving, though no major dents or rust. The paint still has reasonable shine but lacks the depth and gloss of a truly mint example. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; the upholstery shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and the touchpoints, but nothing is torn or broken. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we want you to feel fully confident in your decision. This is a solid, honest used car that has been driven and shows it, but has plenty of life left and represents good value at this price point.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint retains its original deep luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and every panel sits flush with factory-perfect alignment. The interior is equally impressive, showing virtually no signs of wear: the upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are clean and unblemished, and every button, knob, and control functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. The tires have substantial tread remaining, the brakes are responsive and firm, and the suspension feels tight and composed on the road. This is a car you can buy with complete confidence \u2014 it has been meticulously cared for and is ready to serve its next owner without any immediate maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
